      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is for parts or as a major restoration project. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust on the door panels and a large crack in the windshield. Mechanically, the engine requires immediate attention due to a persistent misfire and fluid leaks, and the brakes are near the end of their life. The interior is also heavily worn, with torn upholstery and non-functional climate control. It will need to be towed or undergo extensive repairs before it can be considered reliable for daily use.",
