    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example retains its visceral performance characteristics with a crisp-shifting 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from recent bushing refreshes, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is robust, with documented rod bearing and VANOS services completed. It is a driver-focused machine optimized for throttle modulation and balanced handling.",
      "price": 34500.0,
