    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Luxury Sport SUV that perfectly balances sophisticated style with dependable performance. The exterior features a brilliant metallic finish that has been regularly detailed; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with highway driving, the body is free of any major dents or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort with premium charcoal leather seating that remains firm and supple, showing only light creasing on the driver's bolster. All technological features, including the 10-inch navigation display, heated seats, and the premium 12-speaker audio system, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and delivers smooth acceleration, backed by a comprehensive service history. We recently performed a 60,000-mile service which included a transmission fluid flush, new brake pads, and a fresh set of Continental all-season tires. This is a non-smoker vehicle, consistently garaged, and comes with both original key fobs and all owner manuals. It represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking luxury and reliability without the new-car price tag.",
